common.FinalProjectAPI.chatroom

Interface ICmd2ModelAdapter


  • public interface ICmd2ModelAdapter
    Adapter used by the visitor pattern to send a message to the view. Now in the ICmd2ModelAdapter, it will have access to Mixed-Data Dictionary and will be able to get and put object to and from Mixed-Data Dictionary.
    Author:
    Final Design Group C.
